{"tid":1106584,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"返工俾人搵笨","createTime":"2019-04-14T16:00:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-14T16:25:50.000Z","uid":162332,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"24a1839b2a01e53f4e7a1050b79eee89c3c9623b","tid":1106584,"uid":162332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T16:00:22.000Z","msg":"本身份人好懦弱，好易俾人蝦<br />\n<br />\n今日返工，有個part time 咩撚嘢都唔做，我做埋佢個份，大家都係part time ，我都無岀聲屌佢，因為我懦弱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因爲我傻，點解大家都係同一份糧，我就要傻更更咁做埋佢個份，人地就輕輕鬆鬆咁收工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我好憎我自己咁傻，咁蠢，咩都唔識岀聲，俾人搵笨都受，做到隻狗咁都受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n社會上就係需要我依啲任勞任怨嘅傻仔做最底層<br />\n<br />\n我真係好無用！正廢柴！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點先可以醒小小？"},{"pid":"a4159ad0bd73ae42024c51ba938cd8215d57b5e3","tid":1106584,"uid":31494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T16:20:10.000Z","msg":"人無恥 便無敵"},{"pid":"29080a48ebf75250abdf639eab67949974abf6bc","tid":1106584,"uid":31494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4159ad0bd73ae42024c51ba938cd8215d57b5e3","tid":1106584,"uid":31494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T16:20:10.000Z","msg":"人無恥 便無敵"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T16:25:50.000Z","msg":"「水至清則無魚  人至賤則無敵」。<br />\n君子同小人相比  小人會活得更好 <br />\n因為君子有道德約束  小人卻可以肆意妄為。<br />\n因此只要夠無恥  那麼就天下無敵。"}]}